00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:51.000
We bear the burdens of the ground,

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:53.000
leading the way.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:55.000
We are the ones who have to fight.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:56.000
We are the ones who have to stand the ground.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.000
Leading it, as Helgard.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:00.000
And we do so willingly.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:03.000
As when your older brother and sister followed in my footsteps.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:07.000
Do you understand what I'm telling you, Zanka?

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:13.000
Sir.

00:01:25.000 --> 00:01:26.000
We have undivided powers.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:27.000
Oh, yes, sir.

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:28.000
One thing at a time.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:29.000
Sometimes we meet again.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:46.000
Help!

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:51.959
more deadly than your fellow man. So we stand. As Hellguard, we keep humanity in line.

00:01:52.959 --> 00:01:57.260
What awaits you here at the Central Hellguard Academy is not unlike life on the ground.

00:01:57.620 --> 00:02:00.159
You will be pitted against each other and yourselves.

